**Assessment:** The core architecture is correct, well-structured, and follows established patterns (ESPnet forward contract, SDPA Flash Attention, proper dtype management). The encoder forces FP32 under AMP (preventing NaN). cuDNN SDPA is disabled globally (preventing segfault). These are battle-tested design decisions.

